{"type":"message","id":"e7e8969b","parentId":"efa1a75e","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:17.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring UI Inspiration**\n\nI'm currently diving into Are.na, seeking UI inspiration specifically for a 3/4 isometric \"agent room\" design. My focus is on visualizing a workspace environment, complete with characters at desks and task bubbles that present icons paired with concise text. The design should incorporate 10 to 15 key elements.\n\n\n**Analyzing Visual Styles**\n\nI'm now summarizing the patterns I'm seeing across the gathered references. I'm focusing on color palettes, typography choices, the UI chrome used, the style of icons and bubbles, and how agent states are visualized. The goal is to distill common design elements.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211236478_97","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"isometric \"agent\" workspace UI dashboard inspiration"},"thoughtSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211236568_98","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"site:are.na \"task bubbles\" UI illustration"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211236744_99","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"isometric office \"characters\" UI design patterns","count":10}},{"type":"text","text":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-flash-latest","usage":{"input":45486,"output":681,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46167,"cost":{"input":0.0136458,"output":0.0017025000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0153483}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771211230603}}
{"type":"message","id":"5ea79245","parentId":"e7e8969b","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:17.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search_1771211236478_97","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"isometric \\\"agent\\\" workspace UI dashboard inspiration\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 778,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdmin Dashboard – Agent Management - UI Creative\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://uicreative.net/products/admin-dashboard-template-14\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdmin Dashboard - Agent Management, ... portal, e-commerce, personal business, corporate. <strong>This template is professionally created using Adobe Photoshop, Adobe XD, and Sketch</strong>....\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"October 2, 2023\",\n      \"siteName\": \"uicreative.net\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCase study: Giving Agents better tools by designing Agents' Dashboard | by Ira Winterman | Bootcamp | Medium\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://medium.com/design-bootcamp/case-study-giving-agents-better-tools-by-designing-agents-dashboard-3cd0eea9873d\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAs a Product designer for this project, my goal was to create an intuitive and user-friendly dashboard that would bridge the gap between users’ needs and the company’s business goals. To better understand the Agents&#x27; needs, I conducted both quantitative and qualitative research.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 9, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"medium.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIntroduction | ServiceNow Next Experience\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://servicenownextexperience.github.io/labs/LAB2050-K24-Intro-to-Workspaces/overview/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThrough these exercises you will learn more about how UI Builder works, learn tips and tricks for working with Workspaces, and see best practices applied first hand. ... Exercise 1 - Duplicate the Variant for landing page and add a Data Visualization for HR Agent Workspace · Exercise 2 - Create a new Dashboard page template and add it to HR Agent Workspace\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"servicenownextexperience.github.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAgent Workspace\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.learnnowlab.com/agent-workspace/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nStep 12: Scroll down to the Workspace List related list. ... Using the Record Menu agent can create a new record in Agent workspace interface.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.learnnowlab.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdmin Dashboard - Ticket Agent Perfomance\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://uicreative.net/products/admin-dashboard-template-12\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMobile UI KIT · Mobile Apps · Social Media · Facebook · Instagram · Pinterest · Web Elements · Admin Dashboard · Background · Email Newsletter · Flat Illustration · Hero Header · Isometric · Landing Pages · Pricing Table · Web Banner · Website · Wireframe · Graphics · Esport Logo · Icons · Illustrations · Objects · Home &gt; Products &gt; Web Elements &gt; Admin Dashboard &gt; Admin Dashboard – Ticket Agent Performance ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"October 2, 2023\",\n      \"siteName\": \"uicreative.net\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdd Agent Widgets — Add Your Own Widgets to the Agent Workspace | LivePerson Developer Center\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://developers.liveperson.com/add-agent-widgets-add-your-own-widgets-to-the-agent-workspace.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>The agent workspace default view has five equally-sized widgets, to the right of the chat pane</strong> (see a sample in the screenshot below) — Visit Info, Predefined Content, Page Navigation, Agent Survey, and Conversation History.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"developers.liveperson.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAgent Dashboard designs, themes, templates and downloadable graphic elements on Dribbble\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://dribbble.com/tags/agent-dashboard\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDiscover 28 Agent Dashboard designs on Dribbble. Your resource to discover and connect with designers worldwide.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"dribbble.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdmin Dashboard - Agent Management\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://uicreative.net/products/crm-system-admin-dashboard\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMobile UI KIT · Mobile Apps · Social Media · Facebook · Instagram · Pinterest · Web Elements · Admin Dashboard · Background · Email Newsletter · Flat Illustration · Hero Header · Isometric · Landing Pages · Pricing Table · Web Banner · Website · Wireframe ·\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"August 15, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"uicreative.net\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAgent Workspace page for Performance analytics dashboard.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.servicenow.com/community/next-experience-forum/agent-workspace-page-for-performance-analytics-dashboard/m-p/3097450\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThat component will show the newer platform analytics dashboards: https://docs.servicenow.com/bundle/xanadu-now-intelligence/page/use/par-for-workspace/concept/par-wo...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"November 6, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.servicenow.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nr/servicenow on Reddit: ITSM Agent Workspace - has anyone built this out or know of a demo where I can see a well developed workspace?\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.reddit.com/r/servicenow/comments/g31oru/itsm_agent_workspace_has_anyone_built_this_out_or/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nI can set up UI Policies to hide/show fields but this is a tedious way of trying to make an uncluttered form. I think it is a good idea but severely lacking in features and a bit of a hard sell. I know our service desk agents would reject it almost immediately in favour of the existing interface. ... I&#x27;ve been a strong advocate for it since seeing it at K19. However, we have not moved forward with an implementation as we require dashboard functionality to act as work lists which either introduced in New York or Orlando, I can&#x27;t remember which.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"April 17, 2020\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.reddit.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"isometric \"agent\" workspace UI dashboard inspiration","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":778,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdmin Dashboard – Agent Management - UI Creative\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://uicreative.net/products/admin-dashboard-template-14","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdmin Dashboard - Agent Management, ... portal, e-commerce, personal business, corporate. <strong>This template is professionally created using Adobe Photoshop, Adobe XD, and Sketch</strong>....\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"October 2, 2023","siteName":"uicreative.net"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCase study: Giving Agents better tools by designing Agents' Dashboard | by Ira Winterman | Bootcamp | Medium\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://medium.com/design-bootcamp/case-study-giving-agents-better-tools-by-designing-agents-dashboard-3cd0eea9873d","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAs a Product designer for this project, my goal was to create an intuitive and user-friendly dashboard that would bridge the gap between users’ needs and the company’s business goals. To better understand the Agents&#x27; needs, I conducted both quantitative and qualitative research.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"January 9, 2024","siteName":"medium.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIntroduction | ServiceNow Next Experience\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://servicenownextexperience.github.io/labs/LAB2050-K24-Intro-to-Workspaces/overview/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThrough these exercises you will learn more about how UI Builder works, learn tips and tricks for working with Workspaces, and see best practices applied first hand. ... Exercise 1 - Duplicate the Variant for landing page and add a Data Visualization for HR Agent Workspace · Exercise 2 - Create a new Dashboard page template and add it to HR Agent Workspace\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"servicenownextexperience.github.io"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAgent Workspace\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.learnnowlab.com/agent-workspace/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nStep 12: Scroll down to the Workspace List related list. ... Using the Record Menu agent can create a new record in Agent workspace interface.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.learnnowlab.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdmin Dashboard - Ticket Agent Perfomance\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://uicreative.net/products/admin-dashboard-template-12","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMobile UI KIT · Mobile Apps · Social Media · Facebook · Instagram · Pinterest · Web Elements · Admin Dashboard · Background · Email Newsletter · Flat Illustration · Hero Header · Isometric · Landing Pages · Pricing Table · Web Banner · Website · Wireframe · Graphics · Esport Logo · Icons · Illustrations · Objects · Home &gt; Products &gt; Web Elements &gt; Admin Dashboard &gt; Admin Dashboard – Ticket Agent Performance ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"October 2, 2023","siteName":"uicreative.net"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdd Agent Widgets — Add Your Own Widgets to the Agent Workspace | LivePerson Developer Center\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://developers.liveperson.com/add-agent-widgets-add-your-own-widgets-to-the-agent-workspace.html","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>The agent workspace default view has five equally-sized widgets, to the right of the chat pane</strong> (see a sample in the screenshot below) — Visit Info, Predefined Content, Page Navigation, Agent Survey, and Conversation History.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"developers.liveperson.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAgent Dashboard designs, themes, templates and downloadable graphic elements on Dribbble\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://dribbble.com/tags/agent-dashboard","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDiscover 28 Agent Dashboard designs on Dribbble. Your resource to discover and connect with designers worldwide.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"dribbble.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdmin Dashboard - Agent Management\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://uicreative.net/products/crm-system-admin-dashboard","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMobile UI KIT · Mobile Apps · Social Media · Facebook · Instagram · Pinterest · Web Elements · Admin Dashboard · Background · Email Newsletter · Flat Illustration · Hero Header · Isometric · Landing Pages · Pricing Table · Web Banner · Website · Wireframe ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"August 15, 2024","siteName":"uicreative.net"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAgent Workspace page for Performance analytics dashboard.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.servicenow.com/community/next-experience-forum/agent-workspace-page-for-performance-analytics-dashboard/m-p/3097450","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThat component will show the newer platform analytics dashboards: https://docs.servicenow.com/bundle/xanadu-now-intelligence/page/use/par-for-workspace/concept/par-wo...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"November 6, 2024","siteName":"www.servicenow.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nr/servicenow on Reddit: ITSM Agent Workspace - has anyone built this out or know of a demo where I can see a well developed workspace?\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.reddit.com/r/servicenow/comments/g31oru/itsm_agent_workspace_has_anyone_built_this_out_or/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nI can set up UI Policies to hide/show fields but this is a tedious way of trying to make an uncluttered form. I think it is a good idea but severely lacking in features and a bit of a hard sell. I know our service desk agents would reject it almost immediately in favour of the existing interface. ... I&#x27;ve been a strong advocate for it since seeing it at K19. However, we have not moved forward with an implementation as we require dashboard functionality to act as work lists which either introduced in New York or Orlando, I can&#x27;t remember which.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"April 17, 2020","siteName":"www.reddit.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771211237967}}
