arch\\n---\\nSo pretty much from the start it was clear to me that for the sake of character variety in terms of looks and to save time working on art assets, I&#x27;d somehow have to make a set of character pieces and combine them randomly in the game engine. It proved to be a bit more difficult than it would seem at first glance. Even though principally it&#x27;s the same as combining graphics for a normal side view or top-down 2d sprite, and I had done that plenty of times, there&#x27;s some tricky nuances when doing it with isometric sprites.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 20, 2014\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.indiedb.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n25 Iconset Isometric Character, Icons ft. professional & characters - Envato\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://elements.envato.com/25-iconset-isometric-character-QD2VW5Y\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThis Iconset contains various profession icons/graphic isometric such a firefighter, police, doctor etc., you can use it for any kind of purpose for example hero header, our feature, our services and much more.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"elements.envato.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nUI Design Patterns You Need to Know for Modern Interfaces\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.thedesignership.com/blog/13-ui-design-patterns-you-need-to-know-for-modern-interfaces\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSupporting Icons: Visual symbols used with text or labels in UI design. They provide extra information or emphasis to make it easier for users to understand and interact. ... Make it clear: Your badges should have a straightforward purpose, so users instantly know what they mean. Keep it consistent: Maintain a cohesive design across shapes, colors, and where they appear on your interface. Limit text: If you use text, keep it short. Use one or two characters or easily recognizable icons.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"May 6, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.thedesignership.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"isometric office \"characters\" UI design patterns","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":477,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIsometric Character Graphics, Designs & Templates | GraphicRiver\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://graphicriver.net/isometric+character-in-graphics","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGet 1,847 isometric character graphics, designs &amp; templates on GraphicRiver such as Isometric Characters, Brainstorm Infographic Isometric Characters, Young Adventurer - Isometric Character Sprite\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"graphicriver.net"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIsometric Character Vector Art, Icons, and Graphics for Free Download\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.vecteezy.com/free-vector/isometric-character","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nBrowse 39,883 incredible Isometric Character vectors, icons, clipart graphics, and backgrounds for royalty-free download from the creative contributors at Vecteezy!\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"July 27, 2018","siteName":"www.vecteezy.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nFERE 3D Creative Characters for Web & Mobile UI/UX Design | Figma\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.figma.com/community/file/1300863400628065685/fere-3d-creative-characters-for-web-mobi