ent poses, timing, and techniques to bring your characters and objects to life within the isometric perspective. Implementing isometric sprite sheets in games involves integrating the sprite sheets into your game engine or development environment. Our 2D sprite sheet always contains all the frames of animation arranged in the correct order, usually in a grid pattern.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"July 25, 2025","siteName":"retrostylegames.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIsometric Characters Office Stock Illustrations – 1,492 Isometric Characters Office Stock Illustrations, Vectors & Clipart - Dreamstime\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.dreamstime.com/illustration/isometric-characters-office.html","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIsometric business people groups. Office colleagues conversation. Teamwork office male and female characters 3d vector ... Pharmacy store concept with characters, People ready for vacation, Coworkers in office concept design, set isometric vector\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.dreamstime.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nRandom isometric character generation feature - Office Management 101 - IndieDB\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.indiedb.com/games/office-management-101/features/random-isometric-character-generation","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSo pretty much from the start it was clear to me that for the sake of character variety in terms of looks and to save time working on art assets, I&#x27;d somehow have to make a set of character pieces and combine them randomly in the game engine. It proved to be a bit more difficult than it would seem at first glance. Even though principally it&#x27;s the same as combining graphics for a normal side view or top-down 2d sprite, and I had done that plenty of times, there&#x27;s some tricky nuances when doing it with isometric sprites.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"June 20, 2014","siteName":"www.indiedb.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n25 Iconset Isometric Character, Icons ft. professional & characters - Envato\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://elements.envato.com/25-iconset-isometric-character-QD2VW5Y","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThis Iconset contains various profession icons/graphic isometric such a firefighter, police, doctor etc., you can use it for any kind of purpose for example hero header, our feature, our services and much more.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"elements.envato.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nUI Design Patterns You Need to Know for Modern Interfaces\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.thedesignership.com/blog/13-ui-design-patterns-you-need-to-know-for-modern-interfaces","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSupporting Icons: Visual symbols used with text or labels in UI design. They provide extra information or emphasis to make it easier for users to understand and interact. ... Make it clear: Your badges should have a straightforward purpose, so users instantly know what they mean. Keep it consistent: Maintain a cohesive design across shapes, colors, and where they appear on your interface. Limit text: If you use text, keep it short. Use one or two characters or easily recognizable icons.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"May 6, 2024","siteName":"www.thedesignership.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771211238670}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f23498a","parentId":"44fd6eb9","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:22.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring UI Concepts**\n\nI'm currently focused on identifying relevant UI elements and concepts. I'm prioritizing \"UI chrome\" and \"agent state\" indicators. I've broadened my search terms to include \"virtual workspace UI\" and \"remote office UI,\" aiming to find examples of isometric room designs, plus status indicator icons.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211241612_100","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Gather.town UI dashboard isometric office","count":10},"thoughtSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211241679_101","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"\"Teamflow\" virtual office UI screenshots","count":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211241846_102","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"isometric office \"status bubble\" icon UI"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211242087_103","name":"web_search","arguments":{"count":10,"query":"Habbo Hotel UI design patterns isometric"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"web_search_1771211242189_104","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"site:are.na \"isometric\" \"dashboard\" channel","count":10}},{"type":"text","text":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-flash-latest","usage":{"input":50739,"output":296,"cacheRead":40466,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51035,"cost":{"input":0.0152217,"output":0.0007400000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00303495,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018996649999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771211238682}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ccf5ac3","parentId":"3f23498a","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:22.843Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search_1771211241612_100","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"Gather.town UI dashboard isometric office\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 617,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGather Town Map. Create Immersive Gather Town Maps background image with Icograms Designer: A Powerful Tool for Engaging Virtual Environments\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://icograms.com/usage-gather-town\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDesign isometric city illustrations for urban planning, smart cities, maps, diagrams, zoning &amp; education · Elevate Your Sports Marketing with Icograms Designer: Create Engaging Illustrations for Coaches and Marketing Managers. Transform Your Office Visuals with Icograms Designer: Create Engaging Illustrations\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"icograms.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIcograms Templates - create beautiful isometric diagrams, infographics and illustrations from templates\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://icograms.com/templates/all/gather-town\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCreate your own beautiful isometric diagrams, infographics and illustrations from templates\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"icograms.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDashboard - Gather\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://app.gather.town/dashboard\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGather add-in won’t run in your version of Office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"app.gather.town\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nBored with Zoom? Try Gather Town for Different Virtual Meeting - With Julio\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://withjulio.com/gather-town/bored-with-zoom-try-gather-town-for-a-new-virtual-meeting-experience/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThat is the basic feature of Gather Town, I will explain it afterward, keep going! On the sidebar of Gather, we could see 6 basic bars with 1 feedback bar. I will try to explain all the bars from the bottom to the top. When we click this icon, we would see all the participant that joining our Space. Basically there are two types of Participant Interface, the Remote Office one and the Non-Remote Office one.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"December 17, 2022\",\n      \"siteName\": \"withjulio.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGather | Virtual Workspace for Remote Teams\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.gather.town/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nEverything! For the first 30 days, you can invite up to 50 teammates to try every feature Gather offers. That includes meetings and chat, AI meeting notes, the ability to fully customize your office, and more.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.gather.town\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGet Started | Gather\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.gather.town/get-started\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe newest version of Gather, best for remote teams working together every day in a virtual office. ... The classic version of Gather with event templates. Best for virtual conferences and one-time events. ... Gather 2.0 is a completely new platform, rebuilt from the ground up with a modern, simplified UI and powerful new features for remote teams.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.gather.town\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\ngather.town - The Virtual Office Platform for Remote Team Collaboration\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://eliteai.tools/tool/gather.town\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeams benefit from the ability to personalize avatars and workspaces, embed interactive objects, and manage access through security controls like domain restriction and password protection. With support for up to 500 concurrent users and integrations with tools like Slack, Google, and Outlook, Gather ensures remote teams stay connected, engaged, and aligned—making virtual work more personal and effective.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"eliteai.tools\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow to Create Custom Desk in Gather Town Space - With Julio\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://withjulio.com/gather-town-tutorial/how-to-create-custom-desk-in-gather-town-space/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhen you first step into Gather Town, you’ll notice that each desk in your virtual office is blank. This is where the magic of the “Customize Desk” feature comes in. Just like in a physical office, your desk can become a reflection of who you are.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"August 19, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"withjulio.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGetting Started Guide\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://support.help.gather.town/articles/1982412443-getting-started-guide\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Click and drag to pan around the map or use the zoom controls in the lower right-hand corner</strong>. These settings also let you toggle between Office Views:\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"support.help.gather.town\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGather | Navigating your virtual office just got even easier\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.gather.town/blog/whats-new-3-15-22-navigation-ui\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWe’ve released a brand new app layout, a bigger video grid, and a world-clock extension for collaborating across time zones.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.gather.town\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"Gather.town UI dashboard isometric office","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":617,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGather Town Map. Create Immersive Gather Town Maps background image with Icograms Designer: A Powerful Tool for Engaging Virtual Environments\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://icograms.com/usage-gather-town","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDesign isometric city illustrations for urban planning, smart cities, maps, diagrams, zoning &amp; education · Elevat