"withjulio.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGather | Virtual Workspace for Remote Teams\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.gather.town/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nEverything! For the first 30 days, you can invite up to 50 teammates to try every feature Gather offers. That includes meetings and chat, AI meeting notes, the ability to fully customize your office, and more.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.gather.town"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGet Started | Gather\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.gather.town/get-started","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe newest version of Gather, best for remote teams working together every day in a virtual office. ... The classic version of Gather with event templates. Best for virtual conferences and one-time events. ... Gather 2.0 is a completely new platform, rebuilt from the ground up with a modern, simplified UI and powerful new features for remote teams.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.gather.town"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\ngather.town - The Virtual Office Platform for Remote Team Collaboration\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://eliteai.tools/tool/gather.town","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nTeams benefit from the ability to personalize avatars and workspaces, embed interactive objects, and manage access through security controls like domain restriction and password protection. With support for up to 500 concurrent users and integrations with tools like Slack, Google, and Outlook, Gather ensures remote teams stay connected, engaged, and aligned—making virtual work more personal and effective.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"eliteai.tools"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHow to Create Custom Desk in Gather Town Space - With Julio\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://withjulio.com/gather-town-tutorial/how-to-create-custom-desk-in-gather-town-space/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWhen you first step into Gather Town, you’ll notice that each desk in your virtual office is blank. This is where the magic of the “Customize Desk” feature comes in. Just like in a physical office, your desk can become a reflection of who you are.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","published":"August 19, 2024","siteName":"withjulio.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGetting Started Guide\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://support.help.gather.town/articles/1982412443-getting-started-guide","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n<strong>Click and drag to pan around the map or use the zoom controls in the lower right-hand corner</strong>. These settings also let you toggle between Office Views:\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"support.help.gather.town"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nGather | Navigating your virtual office just got even easier\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.gather.town/blog/whats-new-3-15-22-navigation-ui","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nWe’ve released a brand new app layout, a bigger video grid, and a world-clock extension for collaborating across time zones.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.gather.town"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771211242835}}
{"type":"message","id":"28abf512","parentId":"2ccf5ac3","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:23.335Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search_1771211241679_101","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"\\\"Teamflow\\\" virtual office UI screenshots\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 10,\n  \"tookMs\": 492,\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVirtual Office for Remote Team Collaboration | Teamflow\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow is a virtual office where teams can work, meet and hang out together. It combines video, open spaces, meeting rooms, and tools like docs, whiteboards, video, and images to create a collaborative work space that feels better than working in the office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nFeel Like a Team Again With Teamflow, Your Own Virtual Office\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/blog/announcing-teamflow-feel-like-a-team-again-with-your-own-virtual-office\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIt recreates the casual, unplanned chats and the seamless collaboration that people miss from physical offices. Here’s how it works: you see your video in a bubble on a virtual floor plan. You can move that bubble around, and only hear people around you. That means that, to chat with someone, you just drag your bubble over, and start talking. We’ve been running Teamflow in private beta for the last six months, and were blown away by the response.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVirtual Office for Remote Teams | Teamflow\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/remote-office-software\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow is a virtual office where teams can work, meet and hang out together. It combines video, open spaces, meeting rooms, and tools like docs, whiteboards, video, and images to create a collaborative work space that feels better than working in the office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow | Virtual Office - Upgrade\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/upgrade\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow is a virtual office where teams can work, meet and hang out together. It combines video, open spaces, meeting rooms, and tools like docs, whiteboards, video, and images to create a collaborative work space that feels better than working in the office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow Teamflow build a virtual office using the Daily API\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.daily.co/blog/how-teamflow-keeps-remote-colleagues-connected-building-on-the-daily-api/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow was built on three ideas: spatiality, apps, and persistence. Fundamentally, the app’s UI resembles the floor plan of an office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"November 5, 2021\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.daily.co\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nVirtual Office Coworking Software | Download the Teamflow App\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/download\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWith the Teamflow app, it&#x27;s never been easier to collaborate with your team. Download the latest version for Windows or Mac.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow Reviews 2026: Details, Pricing, & Features | G2\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.g2.com/products/teamflow/reviews\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nWhat problems is Teamflow solving and how is that benefiting you? Makes it easier for our remote-first team to feel more connected. And I like the fun customization aspects, its neat to see different office layouts. Review collected by and hosted on G2.com. ... The reviewer uploaded a screenshot or submitted the review in-app verifying them as current user.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.g2.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow - Virtual Office for your remote team — Steemit\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://steemit.com/steemhunt/@hungryfish/teamflow-virtual-office-for-your-remote-team\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow Virtual Office for your remote team Screenshots Hunter&#x27;s comment Teamflow is a virtual office… by hungryfish\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 13, 2021\",\n      \"siteName\": \"steemit.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHow Teamflow built chat into their virtual office platform\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://talkjs.com/resources/how-teamflow-shipped-a-chat-feature-in-a-few-weeks-with-talkjs/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThey chose TalkJS because of its pre-built UI that offloaded a lot of front-end work as there was no need to design or code the interface from scratch. &quot;We also considered Sendbird and Stream. TalkJS was very easy to integrate and gave us the flexibility we needed.&quot; - Flo Crivello, Founder &amp; CEO at Teamflow · The TalkJS chat API provided the resources to connect all users with private direct messaging and create chatrooms for virtual rooms like the main floor of the office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 6, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"talkjs.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPress\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.teamflowhq.com/press\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nTeamflow is a virtual office platform where teams can work, meet and hang out together. It combines video, open spaces, meeting rooms, and tools like docs, whiteboards, video, and images to create a collaborative work space that feels better than working in the office.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.teamflowhq.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"\"Teamflow\" virtual office UI screenshots","provider":"brave","count":10,"tookMs":492,"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nVirtual Office for Remote Team Collaboration | Teamflow\n<<<END_EXTER