n---\n67 Habbo room ideas\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.pinterest.com/chinjyios/habbo-room-ideas/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n67 Habbo room ideas | isometric art, pixel art, pixel art design · Skip to content · When autocomplete results are available use up and down arrows to review and enter to select. Touch device users, explore by touch or with swipe gestures · Log in · Sign up · Habbo room ideas · 67 Pins ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.pinterest.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPinterest\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.pinterest.com/ideas/habboon-room-ideas/959662588818/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nStardew Valley Room Design · Terraria Storage Room Ideas · 2d Room · See more · Habboon room ideas and more · , 44 Pins · · · , 5d · , 2.6k Pins · · · , 5h · , 321 Pins · · · , 1d · , 52 Pins · · · , 2w · , 121 Pins · · · , 3mo · Habbo Hotel · Isometric Drawing ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.pinterest.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHabbo - pixel art, isometric art, pixel art design - Pinterest\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.pinterest.com/metropi4/habbo/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHabbo Hotel Rooms · Medieval Town Habbo · #Habbo #Pixel #Virtual #Build · Habbo Green Camp House · Medieval House Design Habbo · Habbo Forest Build · Habbo Medieval Theme · Habbo House Inspiration · Habbo Store Ideas · Dark Art Project Ideas · Blood Splatter Art Style · Horror Game Design Inspiration · Habbo Hospital · Habbo Room · Pixel Room · Isometric Bathroom With Blood Splatter ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.pinterest.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHabbo designs, themes, templates and downloadable graphic elements on Dribbble\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://dribbble.com/tags/habbo","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDiscover 10 Habbo designs on Dribbble. Your resource to discover and connect with designers worldwide.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"dribbble.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHabbo Hotel\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.pinterest.com/ideas/habbo-hotel/960852641972/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDiscover Pinterest’s best ideas and inspiration for Habbo hotel. Get inspired and try out new things. 15k people searched this · · · Last updated 2d · Terraria House Design · Game Logo Design · 8 Bit Art · Isometric Building · Acnh Pixel Patterns ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.pinterest.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n9 Habbo hotel inspo ideas | isometric art, sims house ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","url":"https://www.pinterest.com/soosims/habbo-hotel-inspo/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHabbo Room Design With Characters · habbo · Habbo Rooms Ideas · Habbo House Layout · Habbo Hotel Room Layout · Habbo Room Layout · habbo · Dormitorio Futurista · Habbo Hotel · Pixel Art Landscape · Isometric Drawing · Interior Architecture Drawing ·\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT>>>","siteName":"www.pinterest.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771211244279}}
{"type":"message","id":"bd185dcd","parentId":"364b3b84","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:24.517Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"web_search_1771211242189_104","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"site:are.na \\\"isometric\\\" \\\"dashboard\\\" channel\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 0,\n  \"tookMs\": 225,\n  \"results\": []\n}"}],"details":{"query":"site:are.na \"isometric\" \"dashboard\" channel","provider":"brave","count":0,"tookMs":225,"results":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771211244504}}
{"type":"message","id":"568e880f","parentId":"bd185dcd","timestamp":"2026-02-16T03:07:38.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing Patterns Now**\n\nI've got a comprehensive list of references, and I'm diving into summarizing the color palettes I've observed. I'm focusing on the common themes in isometric, virtual office, and classic styles. I will then expand this to other UI style types.\n\n\n**Analyzing UI Trends**\n\nI'm now identifying common elements across these interface styles. I'm noting key aspects such as palette choices (vibrant, limited, with dark mode for tech agents). Typography leans towards sans-serif and high legibility. I'm paying attention to UI chrome, focusing on glassmorphism and rounded designs, plus floating buttons. Icon styles include bubbles and simple glyphs with connection lines, and I'm also examining agent state cues. I am including references now.\n\n\n**Gathering More UI Examples**\n\nI'm now cataloging more visual references. I am focusing on isometric UIs, adding Gather.town, Teamflow, and Habbo Hotel to my examples. I am also gathering tools like Icograms and inspiration from Behance and Dribbble. My current focus is on agent rooms and dashboard UI chrome patterns. I have also included a few more Are.na blocks.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"Researching Are.na and current virtual workspace platforms for 3/4 isometric \"agent room\" UI inspiration reveals a blend of \"toy-like\" 3D dioramas and functional dashboard overlays.\n\n### **Patterns & Design Language**\n\n*   **Color Palettes:**\n    *   **\"Toy Box\" Aesthetic:** High-saturation pastels (mint, coral, lilac) mixed with off-white or soft-grey floors to keep the focus on active elements.\n    *   **\"Command Center\" Dark Mode:** Deep navy or charcoal backgrounds with neon cyan/magenta task bubbles for high-contrast \"agent state\" visibility.\n*   **Typography:**\n    *   **Functional Mono:** Use of monospaced fonts (e.g., *Roboto Mono, JetBrains Mono*) for task IDs or agent stats to convey a \"machine\" or \"system\" feel.\n    *   **Geometric Sans:** High-legibility fonts (*Inter, Poppins*) in small sizes (10-12px) for bubble labels.\n*   **UI Chrome:**\n    *   **Glassmorphism:** Semi-transparent, blurred panels for the main dashboard \"tray\" that sits under or over the isometric room.\n    *   **Thin Strokes:** 1px borders with subtle inner glows to separate the 2D UI from the 3D room.\n*   **Icon/Bubble Styles:**\n    *   **Floating Pills:** Rounded pill shapes (pill-radius: 50px) floating directly above characters’ heads.\n    *   **Connection Lines:** Thin, dashed \"leads\" connecting a task bubble to the specific desk or character.\n    *   **Status Badges:** Small circular icons (ping-pong style) in the bottom-right corner of the task bubble.\n*   **Conveying Agent State:**\n    *   **Active:** Character bobbing animation + vibrant bubble border.\n    *   **Thinking/Busy:** Ellipsis (`...`) bubble or a \"screen glow\" effect on the character's desk.\n    *   **Idle/Away:** Greyscale character filter or a \"Zzz\" particle effect.\n\n### **Top 15 References**\n\n**Are.na Channels & Blocks:**\n*   [Isometric (Alex Nelssen)](https://www.are.na/alex-nelsen/isometric-aupccyx1oyy) – Extensive channel of 3D/Isometric scene references.\n*   [Finance Dark Theme (Block 16825312)](https://www.are.na/block/16825312) – Example of dark UI overlays on isometric structures.\n*   [Vector Isometric Home Rooms (Block 6859412)](https://www.are.na/block/6859412) – Pattern for character-to-room scaling.\n*   [Pixeltemple | Isometric Rooms (Block 36786202)](https://www.are.na/block/36786202) – Strong \"agent room\" aesthetic with vibrant lighting.\n*   [Isometric Office Plan (Block 6859526)](https://www.are.na/block/6859526) – Detailed desk and equipment layouts.\n*   [Low Poly Dental Office (Block 12956573)](https://www.are.na/block/12956573) – Good reference for specialized \"workstation\" assets.\n*   [The Office of Ordinary Things (Block 31650752)](https://www.are.na/block/31650752) – Clean, high-end graphic design approach to isometric branding.\n*   [3D Isometric Living Room (Block 24938051)](https://www.are.na/block/24938051) – Reference for realistic soft lighting in 3/4 view.\n\n**Non-Are.na References:**\n*   [Gather.town](https://gather.town) – The industry standard for virtual office UI and character status bubbles.\n*   [Teamflow](https://www.teamflowhq.com/) – Spatial UI that uses video bubbles on top of floor plans.\n*   [Icograms Gallery](https://icograms.com/templates/all/gather-town) – Massive library of isometric office and dashboard templates.\n*   [Habbo Hotel (Classic UI)](https://habboxwiki.com/Client) – The original blueprint for isometric character chat and status icons.\n*   [Cosmos Video](https://www.cosmos.video/) – Modern, refined spatial UI for remote teams.\n*   [Kumospace](https://www.kumospace.com/) – Focuses on \"spatial audio\" UI cues for agent presence.\n*   [Office Management 101 (IndieDB)](https://www.indiedb.com/games/office-management-101) – Game UI patterns specifically for \"characters at desks\" management.","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-generative-ai","provider":"google","model":"gemini-flash-latest","usage":{"input":57537,"output":1938,"cacheRead":48650,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59475,"cost":{"input":0.017261099999999998,"output":0.004845,"cacheRead":0.0036487499999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025754849999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771211244517}}
